{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.040", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.120", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bienen sind als Best\u00e4uber in der Landwirtschaft und zur Erhaltung der Biodiversit\u00e4t absolut unverzichtbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.400", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb m\u00fcssen und werden wir die Bienen sch\u00fctzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.160", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Europ\u00e4ische Beh\u00f6rde f\u00fcr Lebensmittelsicherheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.160", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "EFSA, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.040", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat ihre Risikobewertung f\u00fcr drei Neonikotinoide, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.480", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich f\u00fcr Clothianidin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.920", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Imidacloprid und Thiamethoxam, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aktualisiert und dabei ein Risiko f\u00fcr Honigbienen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.920", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wildbienen und Hummeln ausgesprochen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.480", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das dabei angewendete Leitliniendokument, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das von der EFSA entwickelte Bee Guidance Document, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.760", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist innerhalb der Mitgliedstaaten umstritten und wird kontrovers diskutiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.680", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weil es zu wenige etablierte Methoden gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um die Auswirkungen auf Solit\u00e4rbienen zu pr\u00fcfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.840", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat die EFSA die Standards von Honigbienen auf Wildbienen angewendet und die Werte um den Faktor 10 erh\u00f6ht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.440", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt kann man trefflich dar\u00fcber streiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.280", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob diese Vorgehensweise korrekt ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allerdings hat unsere Fraktion immer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.200", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch in den vergangenen Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.960", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.960", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Entscheidungen in Zulassungsprozessen auf wissenschaftlicher Basis getroffen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.520", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb werden wir uns der Bewertung der EFSA nicht verschlie\u00dfen und unsere Ministerin Kl\u00f6ckner hier auch unterst\u00fctzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.480", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insgesamt sind in Deutschland 15 Pflanzenschutzmittel zugelassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Neonikotinoide enthalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.920", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vier davon enthalten den Wirkstoff Thiamethoxam. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.160", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie werden als Saatgutbeize vor allem bei Kartoffeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.520", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zucker- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.760", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Futterr\u00fcben angewendet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.600", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Durch die bei uns in der Zulassung festgelegten Anwendungen sind sie als nicht bienengef\u00e4hrdend eingestuft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.200", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ganz einfach deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.760", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Ernte schon vor der Bl\u00fcte erfolgt und die Pflanzen extrem wenig guttieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.720", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das hei\u00dft sehr wenig Wasser absondern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.600", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.680", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir mit den Neonikotinoiden eine weitere Gruppe von Pflanzenschutzmittelwirkstoffen f\u00fcr alle Freilandkulturen verbieten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.520", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann m\u00fcssen wir uns nat\u00fcrlich fragen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.960", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche Alternativen gibt es denn, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.280", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und welche Auswirkungen haben unsere Entscheidungen?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wurde schon angesprochen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.080", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seit dem Verbot der Beizung von Rapssaatgut mit Neonikotinoiden in 2013 ist der Rapsanbau in Deutschland bereits um 100\u00a0000 Hektar zur\u00fcckgegangen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.320", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "trotz auch f\u00fcr die Bienen vielf\u00e4ltiger Vorteile dieser Pflanze. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.280", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sprechen bei Raps n\u00e4mlich von einer Pflanze, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.040", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deren Bl\u00fcte wichtiges Futter f\u00fcr die Bienen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.040", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die f\u00fcr die Biodieselproduktion wesentlich ist und auch als gepresster Rapskuchen eine heimische Tierfuttergrundlage ist und hilft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.080", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sojaimporte erheblich zu reduzieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.320", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht dar\u00fcber hinaus um den Schutz von Hopfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.720", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zuckerr\u00fcben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mais und Kartoffeln. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.720", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zur Bek\u00e4mpfung ihrer Sch\u00e4dlinge wie dem Drahtwurm, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.760", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Rapserdfloh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.840", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Kartoffelk\u00e4fer oder dem Rapsglanzk\u00e4fer gibt es leider nur wenige Alternativen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr den nicht mehr gebeizten Raps beispielsweise werden jetzt Wirkstoffe wie Carbamate und Pyrethroide eingesetzt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.920", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Folge ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.440", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Felder drei- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.480", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bis viermal im Jahr mit diesen Blattinsektiziden gespritzt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.360", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein weiteres Problem im Bereich Pflanzenschutz insgesamt ist bei einer immer geringeren Anzahl an Pflanzenschutzmitteln die zunehmende Resistenz gegen\u00fcber den noch verbleibenden Wirkstoffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.160", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "speziell beim Kartoffelk\u00e4fer und beim Rapsglanzk\u00e4fer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.280", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen nicht auf allen deutschen Kartoffel\u00e4ckern den Asiatischen Marienk\u00e4fer zur Bek\u00e4mpfung des Kartoffelk\u00e4fers ausbringen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.600", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es im \u00f6kologischen Landbau erfolgt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.480", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn der Asiatische Marienk\u00e4fer ist eine invasive Art, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.160", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Folgen seiner Ausbreitung k\u00f6nnen wir zum heutigen Zeitpunkt \u00fcberhaupt noch nicht absehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.560", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "279.320", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dar\u00fcber haben wir schon in der letzten Debatte gesprochen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "279.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.400", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist auch der \u00f6kologische Landbau auf toxische und bienengef\u00e4hrdende Substanzen angewiesen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.960", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was wir brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.720", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eine Risikobewertung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auch bei den Alternativen zwischen Nutzen und Risiken abw\u00e4gt"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.600", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Folgen ber\u00fccksichtigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.880", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sowohl im herk\u00f6mmlichen wie auch im \u00f6kologischen Landbau. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "299.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "311.040", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Notwendig sind eine Strategie und die Beschleunigung von Entwicklung und Zulassungsverfahren alternativer Wirkstoffe und Behandlungsmethoden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "311.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "311.640", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da haben wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "311.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "311.960", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "311.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "313.360", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Konrad, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "313.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.320", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "richtigerweise angesprochen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.800", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen erheblichen R\u00fcckstand, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "319.720", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir dringend angehen m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "319.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.840", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das alleinige Verbot von Wirkstoffen ist weder ein Plan noch eine L\u00f6sung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "325.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "330.520", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir ben\u00f6tigen mehr Weitsicht und eine taktische Vorgehensweise. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "330.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "339.040", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist dieser Antrag der Gr\u00fcnen unzureichend und abzulehnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "339.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.160", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit solchen Antr\u00e4gen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "341.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "343.080", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eher Schaufenstercharakter haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "343.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "346.000", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sch\u00fctzt man weder die Bienen noch die Umwelt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "346.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "347.040", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "347.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "347.840", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "347.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "349.440", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege F\u00e4rber.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
